54.9	Indiana_Jones_and_the_Temple_of_Doom	Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom	Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom is a 1984 American adventure film directed by Steven Spielberg. It is the second (chronologically the first) film in the Indiana Jones franchise and prequel to Indiana Jones and the Raiders of the Lost Ark (1981). After arriving in India, Indiana Jones is asked by a desperate village to find a mystical stone. He agrees, stumbling upon a Kali-worshipping thuggee cult practicing child slavery, black magic, and ritual human sacrifice.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/10/Indiana_Jones_and_the_Temple_of_Doom_PosterB.jpg/220px-Indiana_Jones_and_the_Temple_of_Doom_PosterB.jpg
